Rayalaseema.title: Rayalaseema
Rayalaseema.byline: The Rayalaseema region of Andhra Pradesh in India consists of the districts of Annamayya, Anantapur, Chittoor, Kadapa, Kurnool, Nandyal, and Sri Sathya Sai.

Rayong.title: Rayong
Rayong.byline: Rayong (ระยอง) is a city on the Eastern Gulf Coast of Thailand.
